text: Roxana Condurache (born August 28, 1987 in Iași, Romania) is a Romanian actress."Actriţa româncă Roxana Condurache, nominalizată la premiile Genie, din Canada". RTV Romania, February 18, 2012. She garnered a Genie Award nomination for Best Supporting Actress at the 32nd Genie Awards, for her performance in the Canadian film The Whistleblower. == References == == Other websites == * Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian actors
